{"tid":491829,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【食到絕種】強國人地氈式挖「海知了」 專家：再食要滅絕","createTime":"2017-12-07T01:46:05.000Z","updateTime":"2017-12-07T19:07:10.000Z","uid":39464,"like":23,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":41,"replies":[{"pid":"7baa3509429843deb3ee0b31266d7eb798afbdbe","tid":491829,"uid":39464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-07T01:46:05.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20171206/large/1512566533_f61e.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20171206%2Flarge%2F1512566533_f61e.jpg&h=87a3d1e3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n中國人民以食為天，但也不用將物種食到滅絕！山東青島沿海沙灘棲息着一種當地稱為「海知了」的甲殼類海鮮，專家指牠是介乎蝦和蟹之間的珍貴海洋生物，以腐肉和浮游生物為食，有潔淨海灘的重要生態功能，但近年來卻遭民眾大量挖食，已瀕臨滅絕的威脅。<br />\n<br />\n青島就有人組團到石老人海水浴場附近，挖取「海知了」，而水產工程師在當地電視台節目中提到，這種「海知了」具有營養價值，市民可以放心食用。報道一出，大批民眾開團挖捕，手持鐵鏟與水桶，在海灘地氈式挖掘，大量捕食「海知了」，不僅破壞海灘環境，也造成生態浩劫。<br />\n<br />\n內地記者到石老人海灘所見，三五成群的民眾正在海灘尋找「海知了」蹤跡，一大清早已有豐富的收穫。挖掘「海知了」的民眾均表示，他們第一次見到這種生物，但是對於是否需要保護？他們也沒有頭緒。<br />\n<br />\n有網民指，「海知了」的學名叫做「解放眉足蟹」，並非「蟬蝦」，70年代在青島地域性滅絕，最近物種才有所恢復，4年前又開始在青島沿岸出現，不過報道曝光後，牠們又要面臨地域性滅絕了。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20171206/large/1512568635_76d3.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20171206%2Flarge%2F1512568635_76d3.jpg&h=04056e70&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/china/realtime/article/20171207/57548322\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fchina%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20171207%2F57548322&d=dROWvDezH3xzRK1reZmPt5zN29kXmk9bB7xBuKM86BA%3D&h=4879fb1f\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fchina%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20171207%2F57548322&h=ae7afc3f\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/china/realtime/article/20171207/57548322</a>"},{"pid":"bdebc7e2c2988c1f7957596ba01b7b9c1ab90795","tid":491829,"uid":7125,"like":69,"dislike":2,"score":67,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-07T01:47:37.000Z","msg":"小龍蝦又係<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 食垃圾大果d特別得強國歡心"},{"pid":"0bcc3b7196e4e66e3448706aed7fd69cf42e3436","tid":491829,"uid":44454,"like":1,"dislike":3,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-07T01:49:04.000Z","msg":"海知了有咩營養價值<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"98d8db9d60aa14e51e4d5e58d8dd04ecbc3db0ca","tid":491829,"uid":144323,"like":16,"dislike":5,"score":11,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-07T01:50:59.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>海知了有咩營養價值<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n乜食物都有營養價值架啦"},{"pid":"14f0ab3e31b9f2e5054b1f864e12bae1cfe3b9ac","tid":491829,"uid":68746,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-07T01:52:02.000Z","msg":"海曱甴"},{"pid":"a02d130f306f82aede195df0b12cfe6b6183acbc","tid":491829,"uid":103325,"like":37,"dislike":0,"score":37,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-07T01:59:06.000Z","msg":"幾時新聞會報食屎係無害同埋有營養價值？<br />\n等睇班支那人爭住去食屎"},{"pid":"6c151e480bbe1cd6a8b7f136094e69511b4fae63","tid":491829,"uid":1082,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-07T02:00:15.000Z","msg":"痴撚線<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a4f4de24708696f83da04e0446c285168f7d21f0","tid":491829,"uid":70786,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-07T02:00:16.000Z","msg":"又係支那賤畜<br />\n真係世界毒瘤"},{"pid":"9df2b7e37127ed8854d256a8afeff9529073d4f7","tid":491829,"uid":14918,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-07T02:05:13.000Z","msg":"咩都唔放過<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"aace203125d99e1102cdb0923a6344ace57f895f","tid":491829,"uid":53794,"like":7,"dislike":1,"score":6,"cit